$ON_VEHRAT
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_VEHRAT(zc) From W2HRMAT5
Return

Subprog D_VEHRAT(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
If varinit([M]VEHRAT,indice)=0
 ## Action INILEG
 Call INILEG(VALEUR,"","") From SUBADI
Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

